### CipherTrust API — REST Client test file
### Install VS Code extension: humao.rest-client
### Set @token after login

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@orgId = 1
@consentId = 1
@proofId = 1

# ─── Health ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

# ─── Auth ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Register org admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@testcorp.in",
  "password": "password123",
  "full_name": "Test Admin",
  "role": "org_admin"
}

###

### Register regulator
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "reg@dpdpa.gov.in",
  "password": "password123",
  "full_name": "DPDPA Regulator",
  "role": "regulator"
}

###

### Login (copy access_token → @token above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@testcorp.in",
  "password": "password123"
}

# ─── Organizations ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create organisation
POST {{baseUrl}}/orgs/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "TestCorp Pvt Ltd"
}

###

### List organisations
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get organisation
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{orgId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Register org on Algorand (connect Pera Wallet first)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{orgId}}/register-onchain
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "wallet_address": "YOUR_ALGORAND_WALLET_ADDRESS"
}

# ─── Consent Records ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create consent record
POST {{baseUrl}}/consent/{{orgId}}/records
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "user_identifier": "user123@example.com",
  "consent_type": "data_processing",
  "purpose": "Processing user data for core service delivery under DPDPA Section 7(a)"
}

###

### List consent records
GET {{baseUrl}}/consent/{{orgId}}/records
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Anchor consent on Algorand
POST {{baseUrl}}/consent/{{orgId}}/records/{{consentId}}/anchor
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Revoke consent
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/consent/{{orgId}}/records/{{consentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ─── ZK Proofs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Generate ZK proof
POST {{baseUrl}}/proofs/{{orgId}}/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "proof_type": "consent_compliance",
  "consent_ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

###

### Submit proof on-chain
POST {{baseUrl}}/proofs/{{orgId}}/submit/{{proofId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List proofs
GET {{baseUrl}}/proofs/{{orgId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get proof details
GET {{baseUrl}}/proofs/{{orgId}}/{{proofId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ─── Compliance ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Compliance summary (regulator view)
GET {{baseUrl}}/compliance/{{orgId}}/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Issue compliance certificate
POST {{baseUrl}}/compliance/{{orgId}}/issue-certificate?proof_id={{proofId}}&regulation=DPDPA
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List certificates
GET {{baseUrl}}/compliance/{{orgId}}/certificates
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Verify by Algorand transaction ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/compliance/verify/YOUR_ALGORAND_TXN_ID
